entry.value:
select ana.codice||' - '||ana.nomebreve as station_name, ana.quota as station_hmsl, null::varchar as ident, 'open-trentino' as network, (round(ana.longitudine::numeric, 5)*1e5)::integer as lon, (round(ana.latitudine::numeric, 5)*1e5)::integer as lat, to_char( to_timestamp(substring(dat.dataora,1,10)||' '||substring(dat.dataora,12,19), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')::timestamp - interval '1 hour', 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS"Z"' ) as date,
-- TIMERANGE 1::integer as timerange, 0::integer as p1, 900::integer as p2,
-- VARCODE 'B13011'::varchar as varcode,
-- VALUE per UOM round(dat.misura::numeric, 1)::double precision as value,
-- LEVEL 1::integer as level1, null::integer as l1, null::integer as level2, null::integer as l2
from #{db_schema}.#{db_table_metn_dati} dat join #{db_schema}.#{db_table_metn_logdata} ldat on ldat.batchid = dat.batchid join #{db_schema}.#{db_table_metn_anagrafica} ana on ana.codice = ldat.codice
-- SENSORETIPO where dat.batchid = ${batchid.0} and dat.tipo = 'precipitazioni'
order by dat.dataora;

-- TIMERANGE 0::integer as timerange, 0::integer as p1, 900::integer as p2,
-- VARCODE 'B14198'::varchar as varcode,
-- VALUE per UOM round(dat.misura::numeric, 0)::double precision as value,
-- LEVEL 1::integer as level1, null::integer as l1, null::integer as level2, null::integer as l2
from #{db_schema}.#{db_table_metn_dati} dat join #{db_schema}.#{db_table_metn_logdata} ldat on ldat.batchid = dat.batchid join #{db_schema}.#{db_table_metn_anagrafica} ana on ana.codice = ldat.codice
-- SENSORETIPO where dat.batchid = ${batchid.0} and dat.tipo = 'radiazione'
order by dat.dataora;

select ana.codice||' - '||ana.nomebreve as station_name, ana.quota as station_hmsl, null::varchar as ident, 'open-trentino' as network, (round(ana.longitudine::numeric, 5)*1e5)::integer as lon, (round(ana.latitudine::numeric, 5)*1e5)::integer as lat, to_char( to_timestamp(substring(dat.dataora,1,10)||' '||substring(dat.dataora,12,19), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')::timestamp - interval '1 hour', 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS"Z"' ) as date,
-- TIMERANGE 254::integer as timerange, 0::integer as p1, 0::integer as p2,
-- VARCODE 'B13003'::varchar as varcode,
-- VALUE per UOM round(dat.misura::numeric, 0)::double precision as value,
-- LEVEL 103::integer as level1, 2000::integer as l1, null::integer as level2, null::integer as l2
from #{db_schema}.#{db_table_metn_dati} dat join #{db_schema}.#{db_table_metn_logdata} ldat on ldat.batchid = dat.batchid join #{db_schema}.#{db_table_metn_anagrafica} ana on ana.codice = ldat.codice
-- SENSORETIPO where dat.batchid = ${batchid.0} and dat.tipo = 'umidita_relativa'
order by dat.dataora;

select ana.codice, case when max(dataora_last) is not null then max(dataora_last) else '0000-00-00T00:00:00' end as dataora_last from #{db_schema}.#{db_table_metn_anagrafica} ana left join #{db_schema}.#{db_table_metn_logdata} log on log.codice = ana.codice where ana.fine = '' -- and ana.codice in ('T0405') group by ana.codice order by ana.codice;

insert into #{db_schema}.#{db_table_metn_logdata}(batchutc, codice) values(to_char( to_timestamp(${now():toNumber()}/1000) at time zone 'UTC', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI' ), '${codice.0}') returning batchid;
